{"lemma":"عاهِرٌ","slug":"عاهِرٌ","root":"ع.ه.ر","root_slug":"ع-ه-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ه-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n30883"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a male prostitute, whore"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bitch"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a mercenary","tags":["derogatory"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30883","headword_ar":"عَاهِرٌ","root":"Ehr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An adulterer"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fornicator;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EahorN","text_ar":"عَهْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally an inf. n.]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuhoyarapN","text_ar":"عُهْيَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. in the same sense, as a dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EahorN","text_ar":"عَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to ISh, on the authority of Ru-beh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAhirN","text_ar":"عَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who follows evil, whether by committing adultery or fornication, or by stealing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) or, as in the L,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether by committing adultery"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornication,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by transgressing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any other manner"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quitting the way of truth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"justice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forsaking the command of God;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo faAsiqFA","text_ar":"اَوْ فَاسِقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being put in the L in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aw saAriqFA","text_ar":"او سَارِقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or any one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who does that which induces doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doubt combined with suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euh~aArN","text_ar":"عُهَّارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 131.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwaladu","text_ar":"الوَلَدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilofiraA$i waliloEaAhiri AlHajaru","text_ar":"لِلْفِرَاشِ وَلِلْعَاهِرِ الحَجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, &c.,) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The child is for the master of the bed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA,) meaning, the husband (Msb, TA) of the child's mother, or, if she be a slave, her owner; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and for the adulterer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornicator, disappointment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) meaning, he shall have no right of relationship, (A'Obeyd, S, Mgh, O, Msb,) nor any share in the child: (TA:) like the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu Alt~uraAbu","text_ar":"لَهُ التُّرَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A'Obeyd, Mgh, O, Msb,) which means “ [he has, or shall have, or may he have,] disappointment, ” (Msb,) or “ nothing: ” (Mgh, O, TA:) for some of the Arabs used to establish relationship arising from adultery or fornication; therefore the law annulled this: (Msb:) some, however, explain it agreeably with the apparent [or literal] meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and for the adulterer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornicator, stoning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hjr","text_ar":"حجر"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAhirapN","text_ar":"عَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAhirN","text_ar":"عَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) if not a verbal epithet, [but a possessive epithet meaning properly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu EihorK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ عِهْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,) A woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who comes to a man by night for the purpose of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fujuwr","text_ar":"فُجُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adultery"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornication"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEaAhirapN","text_ar":"مُعَاهِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEaAhirN","text_ar":"مُعَاهِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (CK: [but this is app. a mistake:])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an adulteress"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fornicatress;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEaAhirapN","text_ar":"مُعَاهِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, O) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayoharapN","text_ar":"عَيْهَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) which last is originally ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaharapN","text_ar":"عَهَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamarapN","text_ar":"ثَمَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with an augmentative"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Th, Mbr:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayoharapN","text_ar":"عَيْهَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, and volatile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who does not remain fixed in her place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without continence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, not added by Kr:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EahirapN","text_ar":"عَهِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAhirapN","text_ar":"عَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a woman. (O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA","A","Mgh","Msb","AZ","S","K","Th","Mbr","Kr"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}